comment.body:
@baentsch , 

I noticed that all the other demos that are "docker-ified" are command-line utilities or servers; none of them have GUIs. The only demo that does have a GUI is chromium but it is not "docker-ified" . Perhaps it would be more appropriate if this was done more like chromium and just built without docker? I must admit that my docker know-how is dismal. 

Please let me know your opinion on this matter.
